Before editing admin UI, accounting, expenses, or receipt/proof uploads, read:

- `/ai_context/06_ADMIN_ACCOUNTING_EMAIL.md`
- `/ai_context/03_SECURITY_RULES.md`

Critical rules:

- Admin routes and APIs require authenticated session; verify RBAC on mutations.
- Receipt/proof upload caps in `lib/receiptUploadLimits.ts` must match client compression and API route enforcement.
- Synced order expenses (`flowers`, `delivery`) come from Costs & Profit — do not break `order_id` linkage.
- Automated emails must use Email Control Center (templates + outbox), not ad-hoc Resend HTML.
